<section id="slide-orgd6a802d" data-background="./sos.png" data-background-size="100px" data-background-position="1% 96%" data-background-opacity="0.4">
<h2 id="orgd6a802d">Enter SOS</h2>
<p>
Society for Open Software (SOS) is a newly formed society with the purpose of increasing awareness of free and open source software and boost student engagement with the open source community.
</p>

<div id="org5a92f08" class="figure">
<p><img src="./sos.png" alt="sos.png" width="30%" height="30%" />
</p>
</div>
</section>
</section>
<section>
